abstract: Boston beats Yale, 3-2, in overtime, in first round of NCAA men's hockey tournament; other results noted.
lead_paragraph: Danny O’Regan scored 7 minutes 27 seconds into overtime to give Boston University a 3-2 victory over Yale in the first round of the Northeast Regional in the N.C.A.A. hockey tournament in Manchester, N.H.

headline.main: Boston University Ousts Yale in Overtime
